                        <div class="height5"></div>
                        <div class="float_l">For a ballroom where the chairs will remain on the ballroom floor and where stacking will be minimal, chair covers are not necessary because the wear and tear may be minimal. However, you may want to purchase some chair covers to have on hand for certain chairs that will be stored in a dusty environment or that are transported to other facilities.</div>
